# Maruko sensor kernel modules
#
# Populated by either:
#   scripts/maruko_pull_artifacts.sh drivers   (pull from a known-good device)
#   make -C drivers sensor                     (build from drivers/*.c sources)
#
# Naming convention in this repo:
#   sensor_imxNNN_maruko.ko     ← repo-side filename
#
# The deploy script (scripts/maruko_direct_deploy.sh push-drivers) renames
# these to sensor_imxNNN_mipi.ko when installing under
# /lib/modules/5.10.61/sigmastar/ on the target.
#
# drv_ms_cus_*.ko modules pulled from /lib/modules/5.10.61/sigmastar/ keep
# their original filename.
